descriptionHtml:
MyMovieReview's application you can now check the Latest movies in Kerala (Malayalam, Tamil, Hindi, English), upcoming movies, IFFK movies, ratings, Reviews, Trailers, Posters, Details and More. You can rate and review your favorite movie anytime anywhere!.
App Provides the fastest and easiest way to rate movies on the go!
You can identify top rating movies using this app. Check now running movie details in your location and post your own rating and review.

Check Movies and Reviews !!!
You Too Can Be A Reviewer!
It's Fast And Easy.

Sign in to:

• Rate what you’ve seen


Our mobile app features:

• Now Running Movies in Kerala(Malayalam, Tamil, Hindi, English)

• Movie Reviews

• Movie List Filter Option by languages

• Movie List Sort Option by Release Dates, Rating, Number of Ratings

• Upcoming Movies in Kerala

• Releasing Dates

• Latest Trailers, Videos, Songs, Teasers and more

• Latest Posters, Stills and More

• Previous Movies and Reviews

• Notifications

• Previous IFFK Movies

• Receive notifications for the latest trailers, movie showtimes, and breaking news


Decide what to watch and where to watch it:

• Watch the latest trailers, and clips from movies

• Check movie ratings

• Read user and critic reviews


At MyMovieReview, we take our users' privacy very seriously.

Your Social Information: We only need to read your personal details like mobile number, email id, name, and profile image when you log in to our app, it details will show with your reviews.

When a user makes 50 reviews, then we can make you a verified user

Now running movie ratings currently available only in Kerala. Other states will be added soon.

We are also collecting data from:

BookMyShow
IMDB
IFFK
TicketNew
PVR Cinemas
Carnival Cinemas
Netflix
Moviebuff etc..

Download our app for FREE and post your ratings and reviews at your convenience.

Share My Movie Review app with your friends, if you like it.
